Text: The process is triggered by the demand of a functional department to fill a post.
The post is advertised, applicants apply, the applications are checked and the post is filled.
Constraints extracted: [PRECEDENCE(A=advertise post, B=apply applicant), PRECEDENCE(A=advertise post, B=fill post)]

Text: The process finishes when the post was filled, precisely through the conclusion of a contract of employment.
